'''''Inspectioneering Journal''''' is a technical publication that focuses on [[mechanical integrity]] and reliability issues in the [[chemical industry|chemical]] and [[Petroleum refining processes|refining]] industries.<ref>{{cite news|title=Inspectioneering Journal Description|url=http://www.engineering.com/Products.aspx?page=comp/INS042|accessdate=5 April 2017|work=Engineering}}</ref> It is published bi-monthly. The [[magazine]] was established in 1995 and is based in [[Houston, Texas]].<ref>{{cite web|title=NDT.net Publication Department - Inspectioneering Journal 1995 Index Summary|url=http://www.ndt.net/publicat/bibliog/inspj95.htm}}</ref>

